<section class="gm-dashboard-body"><p>Presets update the system's existing world settings. They never modify Actors or erase campaign data.</p><div class="preset-grid">{{#each presets}}<article class="panel {{#if active}}active{{/if}}"><h2>{{label}}</h2><p>Lethality: {{lethality}} · ammo: {{ammunitionTracking}} · tactical: {{tacticalAutomation}} · situational: {{situationalAutomation}}</p><button type="button" data-apply-preset="{{id}}">Apply preset</button></article>{{/each}}</div><article class="panel"><h2>Current rules profile</h2><p>Lethality {{settings.lethality}} · ammunition {{settings.ammunition}} · tactical {{settings.tactical}} · situational {{settings.situational}}</p></article><button type="button" data-rebuild-all>Rebuild all Core compendiums</button><p><small>Core starships are resources/sample craft. Full ship construction and ship-to-ship rules require the separate <i>Shipyard</i> sourcebook.</small></p></section>
